Title: Hart to Hart: Crimes of the Hart

reviewText: If you're a fan of the Hart to Hart series, then you will like this movie.  Stephanie Powers and Robert Wagner don't disappoint in this made for TV movie.  There is the standard intrigue and romance.  There is such chemistry between "Jonathan and Jennifer".  I love this movie and you will too if you're a H2H fan.
summary: Another great Hart to Hart movie!
Title: Hart to Hart: Crimes of the Hart

reviewText: THIS WAS ONE OF THER BETTER TELIVION SERIES. GREAT STAFF AND ACTIORS AND DIRECTEORS. HUMER AND ACTION. NOT LIKE TV SHOWS TODAY.
Title: Hart to Hart: Crimes of the Hart

reviewText: I liked the movie because of the 2 individuals who were the main characters but the plot was not as good as some of the other movies in the series. The quality was good and if you are a die hard for the main characters it's worth buying and seeing. I would recommend it to anyone who is a fan.
summary: Hart to Hart Crimes of the Heart
